##   rel1: upgraded to 1.0.10, kernels 2.4.32 and 2.4.32-grsec
##   rel8: rebuilt for config changes in 2.4 kernels 2005.11.13
##   rel7: rebuilt for kernel 2.6.14.2-Rubix 2005.11.12
